      <span class="kicker reveal">Our Story</span>
      <h2 class="display reveal d1" style="font-size:clamp(36px,4.4vw,60px);margin:14px 0 22px;line-height:0.92;">Rooted<br />In Place</h2>
      <p class="reveal d1">Gridiron is named after the Gridiron rapids near a family homestead — a stretch of the Kennebecasis that's been part of our story for generations. Family is the heart of this business, and it has grown into something more: a space built on community, connection, and a love for great beer and good company — for all ages and all communities.</p>
      <p class="reveal d2">We brew small-batch craft beer using local New Brunswick and Canadian ingredients whenever possible, complemented by quality ingredients sourced from around the world. Proudly brewed in Hampton, on the shores of the Kennebecasis River — rooted in place, crafted with deep respect for where we come from.</p>
      <div class="story-stats reveal d3">
